channel.title: First guitar (lespaul)
channel.description:
I got bored today so I decided to make a les paul custom which is my favourete guitar I need some tips because I'm kind of clueless on how to make a guitar proper So far I thinks its coming out pretty well if not tell me so :D
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2eyfj82.jpg[/img]
this is what I'm basing it off of: [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2mcifk.jpg[/img]
NOTES: this little chunk down the bottom is just me adding the front of it The picture lost loads of quility in the upload Tell me what to do next Tell Me how I should Do it Thanks Its not much but its a start -jimb
